decks.notes: The key concept of this deck is to utilize Raffine, Scheming Seer as the commander to maximize its potential in an aggro playstyle. The deck focuses on a combination of aggressive creatures and disruptive spells to control the board and deal damage to the opponent. With a mix of evasion, removal, and counterspells, the deck aims to keep the opponent on the back foot while steadily reducing their life total. The inclusion of powerful legendary creatures such as Sheoldred, the Apocalypse and True-Name Nemesis adds additional threats and resilience. The deck also includes fetchlands and dual lands to ensure consistent mana base and access to different colors of mana. Overall, the deck aims to outmaneuver and overwhelm the opponent in a 1 vs 1 format.
